      "title": "Demodara Estate sets an all-time record price",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Demodara Estate, renowned for producing quality liquoring teas achieved an all-time record price of Rs. 2,450 per kg on a BOP grade in the Uva Medium Category at the tea auction held on 19 July. This line of tea was purchased by Akbar Brothers Ltd.",
        "Demodara Estate is located in Badulla and comes under the purview of Hapugastenne Plantations PLC, managed by Browns Plantations. This invoice of tea was marketed and sold by John Keells PLC."
